  "1830110": {
    "name": "THE SIGNAL：塞壬星计划",
    "steam_appid": 1830110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《THE SIGNAL》是一款独特的生存建造游戏。为了寻找失踪的亲人，你不顾一切出发冒险，却意外坠落于一颗陌生的星球——塞壬星。这里充满神秘与未知。为了脱身，你必须在这个复杂的世界中搜集物资、建造设施、开采资源、努力生存，并逐步揭开这颗智慧星球的真正意图，以及——它为何选中你，带你来到这片荒芜星域？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>揭开谜团</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这颗星球为何引你到此？你又能否揭开其背后神秘力量的真相，成功逃离它的掌控？探索未知领域，追寻信号源头，寻找失踪的手足，以及最终——逃出生天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/998116f12daaaabd43f22cbebd2ac15f.webp?t=1771344703\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/998116f12daaaabd43f22cbebd2ac15f.poster.webp?t=1771344703\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与生存</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若想在陌生的塞壬星上生存，你必须持续探索。搜集物资，制作道具，并升级自己的装备。在变幻莫测的环境中，装备是否得当，决定了你能否顺利前行，因此，深入调查星球各处散布的神秘遗迹与坠毁点前，请务必做好准备。或许，这里还有其他幸存者？逐步掌握新技术、开发新资源，用你的制造能力闯出一条生路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/6bbcd84ce72130ea1df2c4b2ba5a95a5.webp?t=1771344703\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/6bbcd84ce72130ea1df2c4b2ba5a95a5.poster.webp?t=1771344703\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开采与适应</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找拥有奇异属性的遗物，并使其回归原位，是揭开塞壬星与及其背后的神秘力量之间深层联系的关键。但是，要让这颗星球重归平衡并非易事。你找到的每一件远古遗物，都可能引发意想不到的变故。只有适应了这里的环境，你才能安全地收集赖以生存的资源和物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/fb26007ea0698ea96f62b10d9a6c3c7e.poster.avif?t=1771344703\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/fb26007ea0698ea96f62b10d9a6c3c7e.webm?t=1771344703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/fb26007ea0698ea96f62b10d9a6c3c7e.mp4?t=1771344703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>研究与制作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解塞壬星及其生态体系，拓展你的生存手段。随着研究的不断深入，你将解锁更多建造与制作的选择、配方、工具、设备和武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/6d60181f20b45a62bb3fbf6c78f1582d.webp?t=1771344703\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/6d60181f20b45a62bb3fbf6c78f1582d.poster.webp?t=1771344703\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义载具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越塞壬星上多个地貌迥异的区域，横跨静谧的林地、密集的沼泽、炽热的裂谷与冰封的苔原。因此，你必须做好周密的规划。对载具进行自定义改装，以穿越这个危机四伏的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/964b18fea8409c12852c0e986b7dcdea.webp?t=1771344703\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830110/extras/964b18fea8409c12852c0e986b7dcdea.poster.webp?t=1771344703\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于GOOSE BYTE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是一支小型开发团队，致力于为玩家打造出奇妙的世界与难忘的体验。我们的工作室于2021年9月成立于加拿大蒙特利尔，并于2023年7月完全独立。《THE SIGNAL》是我们作为团队共同制作的首款游戏，期待与你一同踏上这段精彩的科幻之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
